summary: Live the journey of a young boy guided by fate to become the Skyrim's greatest hero and liberator!
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://userimages-akm.imvu.com/userdata/89/39/10/53/userpics/Snap_khU8EgHNC1820705614.jpg[/img]
[font=Tahoma][color=#cfe2f3][size=4]In this machinima you'll get the answers you wanted from the previous one. Who is the Gray fox? Why he has the cowl? How did he find it? All these questions combined with hard work and respect for the lore this time (as much as I could) defines the New Order. The passion of one man can make the change that world needs? Revolution is coming and the Gray Fox intends to be the leader of it! Have a nice time in this first Patreon-Free episode! [/size][/color][/font]

[color=red][size=5]      Only a small demo will be uploaded here---to see more visit my Channel[/size][/color]
